    "Single host, synthetic workload, fixed query list.",
    "Ranking arithmetic is recomputed from the bounded, digest-bound candidate ledger; candidate generation outside that ledger is not independently rerun.",
    "Three historical turns precede correction or deletion. Their decisions and paths remain reconstructable, but engine re-execution is intentionally excluded because deletion removes canonical plaintext by design.",
